SMS documentation

The project BulkSMS is used to send SMS to multiple person at the same time.

The class SMS contains main method and static method named sendSMS.

We can compose our message in main method and mobile number to send SMS.
The string variables message and numbers in main method is used to store the content of the SMS and numbers is used to store the mobile numbers

The static method sendSMS with parameters message and numbers used to invoke URL connection and send SMS.
This method contains variables apikey, sender, message, route, language, numbers and flash for storing the relevant values for the parameter of the SMS API.
URL connection object is created to invoke connection to the URL to send the message using the SMS API.
